- **Excel (.xlsx)** (if `xlsx` in `--format`): invoke the `xlsx` skill. Two sheets: `Options comparison` (one row per option with costs, benefits, NPV, BCR, test results) and `SCM calculation` (Standard Cost Model working with blue input cells). Save as `ria-[slug]-[date].xlsx`.
- **Word (.docx)** (if `word` in `--format`): invoke the `docx` skill. One document, the full RIA structure with cover page, hyperlinked references. Save as `ria-[slug]-[date].docx`.
